Name: Twee Zwaantjes
Review Text: Super nice bar near the canal, the waitress lady is super friendly and kind, the atmosphere inside cozy, and the mulled wine was amazing!

Name: Twee Zwaantjes
Review Text: One of the coolest brown cafe in Amsterdam! I always enjoy the music from Amsterdam! The happy people! And the beers. One evening in de twee zwaantjes and your whole week is good!

Name: Twee Zwaantjes
Review Text: Now this a real Amsterdam Cafe , like it was for a century. Reat hospitality, no mather where you come from, as you bring a good mood. And are in for a beer and cheer. Jossie the owner is the real thing. Lots of humor, and nice friedly good looking girls behind the bar. Prices are modest. Have a great time.

Name: Twee Zwaantjes
Review Text: Good place to get a beer and hang out. With outdoor or indoor seating it fits the weather. The waiter is very nice and helpful, fun to chat with. Service is fast and the drinks aren't badly price.
